name: Roman Balochi
heroTitle: Yak madadgaren o asan en Balochi Labzbalad
heroSub: Ae Labzbalad yak autharitya che maintain nahen. Pameshka dast nakapage umeed hast. Yak labze dast nakapage halata shumara gon dast bandi en ke hama labza jama bekane gon. Minnatwar!
howToAddWord: Yake noken lapze jama kanage wasta ae allami en ke kam az kam yak zubane toka hama labz dayag bebi.
